lead_paragraph: Cincinnati coach Mick Cronin preaches to his team the importance of finding ways to win when you're not hitting shots. Wednesday night's victory over Temple could be Exhibit A of his mantra.

headline.print_headline: Clark, Evans Lead No. 23 Cincinnati Past Temple
